ate to spectra of extreme events that can predict irradiance across a\nwide wavelength range including unobserved wavelengths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2020 19:29:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 22:40:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-27"}
