utionary Bat Algorithm is a promising meta-heuristic for solving\nEvolutionary Multitasking scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 13:37:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-30"}
